production of onshore oil natural gas coal natural gas liquids and related products within the midstream sector it focuses on gathering processing storage terminals and transportation of oil natural gas coal pipeline and related products in the transmission sector the firm invests in interstate and intrastate gas and electric transportation systems within the distribution sector it invests in electric and gas distribution companies and related businesses the firm primarily invests in companies based in north america western europe australia and new zealand it typically invests between  million and  million in its portfolio companies with enterprise value of more than  million arclight capital partners llc was founded in  and is based in boston massachusetts with additional offices in new york new york and luxembourg luxembourg detailed description  clarendon streetth floorboston ma united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwarclightcapitalcom key executives for arclight capital partners llc mr daniel r revers managing partner partner and cofounder age  mr robb e turner senior partner and cofounder age  mr robert m trevisani cpa chief financial officer mr thomas g kilgore head of risk management and chief compliance officer mr theodore d burke jd partner and general counsel age  compensation as of fiscal year  arclight capital partners llc key developments arclight capital to purchase transcanadas new england hydroelectric power portfolio nov   arclight capital partners announced that its affiliate great river hydro signed a definitive agreement to acquire transcanadas new england hydroelectric power portfolio with  facilities on the connecticut and deerfield rivers in vermont new hampshire and massachusetts transcanadas  mw renewable power portfolio is the large conventional hydro system in new england the portfolio includes the  mw moore facility and  other facilities totaling  mw the transaction is expected to close in mid subject to customary regulatory and other ap